Tega Tosin Richard (amụrụ na 13 Novemba 1992) bụ nwaanyị na-eme egwuregwu igba-mgba.  O sonyere n'egwuregwu Commonwealth na 2010 ma nweta ọla nchara na mmemme nke nwanyi nke 59kg freestyle. O nwetakwara ihe nrite ọla ọcha na mmemme nke ụmụ nwanyị 63kg freestyle na egwuregwu mgba nke asọmpi Afrika na 2010.
